c: 19
v: 58
t: "Ko …ìen woni …ìen, …ìe Alla Neemini e dow mu'un immorde e Annabaa…ìe ka ge…óal …ìebibbe Aadama e …ìen …ìe Men wa…ó…óinnoo wonndude e Nuuhu e ge…óal…ìe Ibraahiima e Israa'iila e …ìen …ìe Men Fewni Men Su…ìii si janngaama e dow ma…ì…ìe Aayeeje Hinnorante …ìe fukko ko…ìe sujjoo…ìe e wulloo…ìe. @Corrected"